claim.claim-text:
1. A backlight module, comprising a first optical film, a second optical film and a backplate frame, wherein the backlight module further comprises an optical film supporting device for splicing and supporting the first optical film and the second optical film, the optical film supporting device comprising:
a body;
a splicing portion for splicing and supporting the first optical film and the second optical film; and
a fixing portion fixed to the backplate frame;
wherein the optical film supporting device is made of a transparent material.

9. A liquid crystal display (LCD) device, comprising a liquid crystal panel and a backlight module, wherein the backlight module comprises a first optical film, a second optical film and a backplate frame, and the backlight module further comprising an optical film supporting device for splicing and supporting the first optical film and the second optical film, the optical film supporting device comprising:
a body;
a splicing portion for splicing and supporting the first optical film and the second optical film; and
a fixing portion fixed to the backplate frame;
wherein the optical film supporting device is made of a transparent material.
